'|url=http://blogs.laweekly.com/westcoastsound/2012/04/exclusive_track_ancestors_new.php|accessdate=19 April 2012|newspaper=[[LA Weekly]]|publisher=[[Village Voice Media]]|date=2 April 2012}}</ref>\n* [[Archivist (band)|Archivist]]<ref name=\"EnD\">{{cite web|url=https://www.echoesanddust.com/2017/04/archivist-construct/|title=Archivist \u2013 ''Construct''|last=Butler|first=Matt|publisher=Echoes and Dust|date=30 April 2017|accessdate=1 March 2019}}</ref>\n* [[Astronoid]]<ref>{{cite web |last1=Nelson |first1=Michael |title=Band To Watch: Astronoid |url=https://www.stereogum.com/1880105/band-to-watch-astronoid/franchises/band-to-watch/ |website=Stereogum |accessdate=10 November 2018}}</ref>\n\n'''B'''\n* [[Battle of Mice]]<ref>True, Chris. [http://www.allmusic.com/artist/battle-of-mice-p783686 \"Battle of Mice\"]. [[AllMusic]]. Retrieved 27 November 2011.</ref>\n* [[The Black Heart Rebellion]]<ref name=\"fmz\">{{cite web|url=http://www.fullmoonzine.cz/novinky/the-black-heart-rebellion-se-vraci|title=The Black Heart Rebellion se vrac\u00ed|trans-title=The Black Heart Rebellion return|language=Czech|publisher=Full Moon|date=7 January 2019|accessdate=5 March 2019}}</ref>\n* [[Boris (band)|Boris]]<ref name=\"nyt1\">{{cite news | last = Caraminica | first = Jon | url = http://www.iht.com/articles/2005/09/19/features/heavy.php | title = The alchemy of art-world heavy metal | newspaper = [[The New York Times]] | accessdate = 20 September 2005}}</ref>\n* [[Burst (band)|Burst]]<ref name=\"burst\">{{cite magazine | first = Aaron | last = Burgess | url = http://altpress.com/reviews/173.htm | title = The loveliest album to crush our skull in months | magazine = [[Alternative Press (music magazine)|Alternative Press]] | accessdate = 29 January 2008 | date = 23 May 2006 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110809212036/http://www.altpress.com/reviews/173.htm | archive-date = 2011-08-09 | url-status = dead }}</ref>\n\n'''C'''\n* [[Callisto (band)|Callisto]]<ref>{{cite web|